- Wind shifted the post. - Ah!
風で柱が ずれたのよ

163
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:14,365
Mmm! That's good pork!
おいしい豚肉

164
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,483
Oh! I didn't mean... I wasn't...
違うのよ...えっと

165
